1389#if USE(BIGINT32)
1390void SpeculativeJIT::speculateBigInt32(Edge edge)
1391{
1392 if (!needsTypeCheck(edge, SpecBigInt32))
1393 return;
1394
1395 (SpeculateBigInt32Operand(this, edge)).gpr();
1396}
1397
1398void SpeculativeJIT::speculateAnyBigInt(Edge edge)
1399{
1400 if (!needsTypeCheck(edge, SpecBigInt))
1401 return;
1402
1403 JSValueOperand value(this, edge, ManualOperandSpeculation);
1404 JSValueRegs valueRegs = value.jsValueRegs();
1405 GPRTemporary temp(this);
1406 GPRReg tempGPR = temp.gpr();
1407 JITCompiler::Jump notCell = m_jit.branchIfNotCell(valueRegs);
1408 // I inlined speculateHeapBigInt because it would be incorrect to call it here if it did JSValueOperand / SpeculateXXXOperand,
1409 // as it would confuse the DFG register allocator.
1410 DFG_TYPE_CHECK(valueRegs, edge, ~SpecCellCheck | SpecHeapBigInt, m_jit.branchIfNotHeapBigInt(valueRegs.gpr()));
1411 auto done = m_jit.jump();
1412 notCell.link(&m_jit);
1413 DFG_TYPE_CHECK(valueRegs, edge, SpecCellCheck | SpecBigInt32, m_jit.branchIfNotBigInt32(valueRegs.gpr(), tempGPR));
1414 done.link(&m_jit);
1415}
1416
1417GPRReg SpeculativeJIT::fillSpeculateBigInt32(Edge edge)
1418{
1419 AbstractValue& value = m_state.forNode(edge);
1420 SpeculatedType type = value.m_type;
1421
1422 m_interpreter.filter(value, SpecBigInt32);
1423 if (value.isClear()) {
1424 if (mayHaveTypeCheck(edge.useKind()))
1425 terminateSpeculativeExecution(Uncountable, JSValueRegs(), nullptr);
1426 return allocate();
1427 }
1428
1429 VirtualRegister virtualRegister = edge->virtualRegister();
1430 GenerationInfo& info = generationInfoFromVirtualRegister(virtualRegister);
1431
1432 switch (info.registerFormat()) {
1433 case DataFormatNone: {
1434 GPRReg gpr = allocate();
1435
1436 if (edge->hasConstant()) {
1437 JSValue jsValue = edge->asJSValue();
1438 m_gprs.retain(gpr, virtualRegister, SpillOrderConstant);
1439 ASSERT(jsValue.isBigInt32());
1440 m_jit.move(MacroAssembler::TrustedImm64(JSValue::encode(jsValue)), gpr);
1441 info.fillJSValue(*m_stream, gpr, DataFormatJSBigInt32);
1442 return gpr;
1443 }
1444
1445 DataFormat spillFormat = info.spillFormat();
1446 DFG_ASSERT(m_jit.graph(), m_currentNode, (spillFormat & DataFormatJS) || spillFormat == DataFormatBigInt32, spillFormat);
1447
1448 m_gprs.retain(gpr, virtualRegister, SpillOrderSpilled);
1449
1450 if (spillFormat == DataFormatBigInt32) {
1451 // We have not yet implemented this
1452 RELEASE_ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1453 }
1454 if (spillFormat == DataFormatJSBigInt32) {
1455 m_jit.load64(JITCompiler::addressFor(virtualRegister), gpr);
1456 info.fillJSValue(*m_stream, gpr, DataFormatJSBigInt32);
1457 return gpr;
1458 }
1459
1460 m_jit.load64(JITCompiler::addressFor(virtualRegister), gpr);
1461
1462 info.fillJSValue(*m_stream, gpr, DataFormatJS);
1463 m_gprs.unlock(gpr);
1464 FALLTHROUGH;
1465 }
1466
1467 case DataFormatJS: {
1468 GPRReg gpr = info.gpr();
1469 m_gprs.lock(gpr);
1470 if (type & ~SpecBigInt32) {
1471 CCallHelpers::JumpList failureCases;
1472 GPRReg tempGPR = allocate();
1473 failureCases.append(m_jit.branchIfNotBigInt32(gpr, tempGPR));
1474 speculationCheck(BadType, JSValueRegs(gpr), edge, failureCases);
1475 unlock(tempGPR);
1476 }
1477 info.fillJSValue(*m_stream, gpr, DataFormatJSBigInt32);
1478 return gpr;
1479 }
1480
1481 case DataFormatJSBigInt32: {
1482 GPRReg gpr = info.gpr();
1483 m_gprs.lock(gpr);
1484 return gpr;
1485 }
1486
1487 case DataFormatBoolean:
1488 case DataFormatJSBoolean:
1489 case DataFormatJSInt32:
1490 case DataFormatInt32:
1491 case DataFormatJSDouble:
1492 case DataFormatJSCell:
1493 case DataFormatCell:
1494 case DataFormatDouble:
1495 case DataFormatStorage:
1496 case DataFormatInt52:
1497 case DataFormatStrictInt52:
1498 case DataFormatBigInt32:
1499 DFG_CRASH(m_jit.graph(), m_currentNode, "Bad data format");
1500
1501 default:
1502 DFG_CRASH(m_jit.graph(), m_currentNode, "Corrupt data format");
1503 return InvalidGPRReg;
1504 }
1505}
1506#endif // USE(BIGINT32)
1507
1508void SpeculativeJIT::compileObjectStrictEquality(Edge objectChild, Edge otherChild)
1509{
1510 SpeculateCellOperand op1(this, objectChild);
1511 JSValueOperand op2(this, otherChild);
1512 GPRTemporary result(this);
1513
1514 GPRReg op1GPR = op1.gpr();
1515 GPRReg op2GPR = op2.gpr();
1516 GPRReg resultGPR = result.gpr();
1517
1518 DFG_TYPE_CHECK(JSValueSource::unboxedCell(op1GPR), objectChild, SpecObject, m_jit.branchIfNotObject(op1GPR));
1519
1520 // At this point we know that we can perform a straight-forward equality comparison on pointer
1521 // values because we are doing strict equality.
1522 m_jit.compare64(MacroAssembler::Equal, op1GPR, op2GPR, resultGPR);
1523 m_jit.or32(TrustedImm32(JSValue::ValueFalse), resultGPR);
1524 jsValueResult(resultGPR, m_currentNode, DataFormatJSBoolean);
1525}
1526
1527void SpeculativeJIT::compilePeepHoleObjectStrictEquality(Edge objectChild, Edge otherChild, Node* branchNode)
1528{
1529 BasicBlock* taken = branchNode->branchData()->taken.block;
1530 BasicBlock* notTaken = branchNode->branchData()->notTaken.block;
1531
1532 SpeculateCellOperand op1(this, objectChild);
1533 JSValueOperand op2(this, otherChild);
1534
1535 GPRReg op1GPR = op1.gpr();
1536 GPRReg op2GPR = op2.gpr();
1537
1538 DFG_TYPE_CHECK(JSValueSource::unboxedCell(op1GPR), objectChild, SpecObject, m_jit.branchIfNotObject(op1GPR));
1539
1540 if (taken == nextBlock()) {
1541 branchPtr(MacroAssembler::NotEqual, op1GPR, op2GPR, notTaken);
1542 jump(taken);
1543 } else {
1544 branchPtr(MacroAssembler::Equal, op1GPR, op2GPR, taken);
1545 jump(notTaken);
1546 }
1547}
1548
1549void SpeculativeJIT::compileObjectToObjectOrOtherEquality(Edge leftChild, Edge rightChild)
1550{
1551 SpeculateCellOperand op1(this, leftChild);
1552 JSValueOperand op2(this, rightChild, ManualOperandSpeculation);
1553 GPRTemporary result(this);
1554
1555 GPRReg op1GPR = op1.gpr();
1556 GPRReg op2GPR = op2.gpr();
1557 GPRReg resultGPR = result.gpr();
1558
1559 bool masqueradesAsUndefinedWatchpointValid =
1560 masqueradesAsUndefinedWatchpointIsStillValid();
1561
1562 if (masqueradesAsUndefinedWatchpointValid) {
1563 DFG_TYPE_CHECK(
1564 JSValueSource::unboxedCell(op1GPR), leftChild, SpecObject, m_jit.branchIfNotObject(op1GPR));
1565 } else {
1566 DFG_TYPE_CHECK(
1567 JSValueSource::unboxedCell(op1GPR), leftChild, SpecObject, m_jit.branchIfNotObject(op1GPR));
1568 speculationCheck(BadType, JSValueSource::unboxedCell(op1GPR), leftChild,
1569 m_jit.branchTest8(
1570 MacroAssembler::NonZero,
1571 MacroAssembler::Address(op1GPR, JSCell::typeInfoFlagsOffset()),
1572 MacroAssembler::TrustedImm32(MasqueradesAsUndefined)));
1573 }
1574
1575 // It seems that most of the time when programs do a == b where b may be either null/undefined
1576 // or an object, b is usually an object. Balance the branches to make that case fast.
1577 MacroAssembler::Jump rightNotCell = m_jit.branchIfNotCell(JSValueRegs(op2GPR));
1578
1579 // We know that within this branch, rightChild must be a cell.
1580 if (masqueradesAsUndefinedWatchpointValid) {
1581 DFG_TYPE_CHECK(
1582 JSValueRegs(op2GPR), rightChild, (~SpecCellCheck) | SpecObject, m_jit.branchIfNotObject(op2GPR));
1583 } else {
1584 DFG_TYPE_CHECK(
1585 JSValueRegs(op2GPR), rightChild, (~SpecCellCheck) | SpecObject, m_jit.branchIfNotObject(op2GPR));
1586 speculationCheck(BadType, JSValueRegs(op2GPR), rightChild,
1587 m_jit.branchTest8(
1588 MacroAssembler::NonZero,
1589 MacroAssembler::Address(op2GPR, JSCell::typeInfoFlagsOffset()),
1590 MacroAssembler::TrustedImm32(MasqueradesAsUndefined)));
1591 }
1592
1593 // At this point we know that we can perform a straight-forward equality comparison on pointer
1594 // values because both left and right are pointers to objects that have no special equality
1595 // protocols.
1596 m_jit.compare64(MacroAssembler::Equal, op1GPR, op2GPR, resultGPR);
1597 MacroAssembler::Jump done = m_jit.jump();
1598
1599 rightNotCell.link(&m_jit);
1600
1601 // We know that within this branch, rightChild must not be a cell. Check if that is enough to
1602 // prove that it is either null or undefined.
1603 if (needsTypeCheck(rightChild, SpecCellCheck | SpecOther)) {
1604 m_jit.move(op2GPR, resultGPR);
1605 m_jit.and64(MacroAssembler::TrustedImm32(~JSValue::UndefinedTag), resultGPR);
1606
1607 typeCheck(
1608 JSValueRegs(op2GPR), rightChild, SpecCellCheck | SpecOther,
1609 m_jit.branch64(
1610 MacroAssembler::NotEqual, resultGPR,
1611 MacroAssembler::TrustedImm64(JSValue::ValueNull)));
1612 }
1613 m_jit.move(TrustedImm32(0), result.gpr());
1614
1615 done.link(&m_jit);
1616 m_jit.or32(TrustedImm32(JSValue::ValueFalse), resultGPR);
1617 jsValueResult(resultGPR, m_currentNode, DataFormatJSBoolean);
1618}
1619
1620void SpeculativeJIT::compilePeepHoleObjectToObjectOrOtherEquality(Edge leftChild, Edge rightChild, Node* branchNode)
1621{
1622 BasicBlock* taken = branchNode->branchData()->taken.block;
1623 BasicBlock* notTaken = branchNode->branchData()->notTaken.block;
1624
1625 SpeculateCellOperand op1(this, leftChild);
1626 JSValueOperand op2(this, rightChild, ManualOperandSpeculation);
1627 GPRTemporary result(this);
1628
1629 GPRReg op1GPR = op1.gpr();
1630 GPRReg op2GPR = op2.gpr();
1631 GPRReg resultGPR = result.gpr();
1632
1633 bool masqueradesAsUndefinedWatchpointValid =
1634 masqueradesAsUndefinedWatchpointIsStillValid();
1635
1636 if (masqueradesAsUndefinedWatchpointValid) {
1637 DFG_TYPE_CHECK(
1638 JSValueSource::unboxedCell(op1GPR), leftChild, SpecObject, m_jit.branchIfNotObject(op1GPR));
1639 } else {
1640 DFG_TYPE_CHECK(
1641 JSValueSource::unboxedCell(op1GPR), leftChild, SpecObject, m_jit.branchIfNotObject(op1GPR));
1642 speculationCheck(BadType, JSValueSource::unboxedCell(op1GPR), leftChild,
1643 m_jit.branchTest8(
1644 MacroAssembler::NonZero,
1645 MacroAssembler::Address(op1GPR, JSCell::typeInfoFlagsOffset()),
1646 MacroAssembler::TrustedImm32(MasqueradesAsUndefined)));
1647 }
1648
1649 // It seems that most of the time when programs do a == b where b may be either null/undefined
1650 // or an object, b is usually an object. Balance the branches to make that case fast.
1651 MacroAssembler::Jump rightNotCell = m_jit.branchIfNotCell(JSValueRegs(op2GPR));
1652
1653 // We know that within this branch, rightChild must be a cell.
1654 if (masqueradesAsUndefinedWatchpointValid) {
1655 DFG_TYPE_CHECK(
1656 JSValueRegs(op2GPR), rightChild, (~SpecCellCheck) | SpecObject, m_jit.branchIfNotObject(op2GPR));
1657 } else {
1658 DFG_TYPE_CHECK(
1659 JSValueRegs(op2GPR), rightChild, (~SpecCellCheck) | SpecObject, m_jit.branchIfNotObject(op2GPR));
1660 speculationCheck(BadType, JSValueRegs(op2GPR), rightChild,
1661 m_jit.branchTest8(
1662 MacroAssembler::NonZero,
1663 MacroAssembler::Address(op2GPR, JSCell::typeInfoFlagsOffset()),
1664 MacroAssembler::TrustedImm32(MasqueradesAsUndefined)));
1665 }
1666
1667 // At this point we know that we can perform a straight-forward equality comparison on pointer
1668 // values because both left and right are pointers to objects that have no special equality
1669 // protocols.
1670 branch64(MacroAssembler::Equal, op1GPR, op2GPR, taken);
1671
1672 // We know that within this branch, rightChild must not be a cell. Check if that is enough to
1673 // prove that it is either null or undefined.
1674 if (!needsTypeCheck(rightChild, SpecCellCheck | SpecOther))
1675 rightNotCell.link(&m_jit);
1676 else {
1677 jump(notTaken, ForceJump);
1678
1679 rightNotCell.link(&m_jit);
1680 m_jit.move(op2GPR, resultGPR);
1681 m_jit.and64(MacroAssembler::TrustedImm32(~JSValue::UndefinedTag), resultGPR);
1682
1683 typeCheck(
1684 JSValueRegs(op2GPR), rightChild, SpecCellCheck | SpecOther, m_jit.branch64(
1685 MacroAssembler::NotEqual, resultGPR,
1686 MacroAssembler::TrustedImm64(JSValue::ValueNull)));
1687 }
1688
1689 jump(notTaken);
1690}
1691
1692void SpeculativeJIT::compileSymbolUntypedEquality(Node* node, Edge symbolEdge, Edge untypedEdge)
1693{
1694 SpeculateCellOperand symbol(this, symbolEdge);
1695 JSValueOperand untyped(this, untypedEdge);
1696 GPRTemporary result(this, Reuse, symbol, untyped);
1697
1698 GPRReg symbolGPR = symbol.gpr();
1699 GPRReg untypedGPR = untyped.gpr();
1700 GPRReg resultGPR = result.gpr();
1701
1702 speculateSymbol(symbolEdge, symbolGPR);
1703
1704 // At this point we know that we can perform a straight-forward equality comparison on pointer
1705 // values because we are doing strict equality.
1706 m_jit.compare64(MacroAssembler::Equal, symbolGPR, untypedGPR, resultGPR);
1707 unblessedBooleanResult(resultGPR, node);
1708}
1709
1710void SpeculativeJIT::compileInt52Compare(Node* node, MacroAssembler::RelationalCondition condition)
1711{
1712 SpeculateWhicheverInt52Operand op1(this, node->child1());
1713 SpeculateWhicheverInt52Operand op2(this, node->child2(), op1);
1714 GPRTemporary result(this, Reuse, op1, op2);
1715
1716 m_jit.compare64(condition, op1.gpr(), op2.gpr(), result.gpr());
1717
1718 // If we add a DataFormatBool, we should use it here.
1719 m_jit.or32(TrustedImm32(JSValue::ValueFalse), result.gpr());
1720 jsValueResult(result.gpr(), m_currentNode, DataFormatJSBoolean);
1721}
1722
1723void SpeculativeJIT::compilePeepHoleInt52Branch(Node* node, Node* branchNode, JITCompiler::RelationalCondition condition)
1724{
1725 BasicBlock* taken = branchNode->branchData()->taken.block;
1726 BasicBlock* notTaken = branchNode->branchData()->notTaken.block;
1727
1728 // The branch instruction will branch to the taken block.
1729 // If taken is next, switch taken with notTaken & invert the branch condition so we can fall through.
1730 if (taken == nextBlock()) {
1731 condition = JITCompiler::invert(condition);
1732 BasicBlock* tmp = taken;
1733 taken = notTaken;
1734 notTaken = tmp;
1735 }
1736
1737 SpeculateWhicheverInt52Operand op1(this, node->child1());
1738 SpeculateWhicheverInt52Operand op2(this, node->child2(), op1);
1739
1740 branch64(condition, op1.gpr(), op2.gpr(), taken);
1741 jump(notTaken);
1742}
1743
1744#if USE(BIGINT32)
1745void SpeculativeJIT::compileBigInt32Compare(Node* node, MacroAssembler::RelationalCondition condition)
1746{
1747 SpeculateBigInt32Operand op1(this, node->child1());
1748 SpeculateBigInt32Operand op2(this, node->child2());
1749 GPRTemporary result(this, Reuse, op1, op2);
1750
1751 GPRReg op1GPR = op1.gpr();
1752 GPRReg op2GPR = op2.gpr();
1753 GPRReg resultGPR = result.gpr();
1754
1755 if (condition == MacroAssembler::Equal || condition == MacroAssembler::NotEqual) {
1756 // No need to unbox the operands, since the tag bits are identical
1757 m_jit.compare64(condition, op1GPR, op2GPR, resultGPR);
1758 } else {
1759 GPRTemporary temp(this);
1760 GPRReg tempGPR = temp.gpr();
1761
1762 m_jit.unboxBigInt32(op1GPR, tempGPR);
1763 m_jit.unboxBigInt32(op2GPR, resultGPR);
1764 m_jit.compare32(condition, tempGPR, resultGPR, resultGPR);
1765 }
1766 unblessedBooleanResult(resultGPR, node);
1767}
1768
1769void SpeculativeJIT::compilePeepHoleBigInt32Branch(Node* node, Node* branchNode, JITCompiler::RelationalCondition condition)
1770{
1771 BasicBlock* taken = branchNode->branchData()->taken.block;
1772 BasicBlock* notTaken = branchNode->branchData()->notTaken.block;
1773
1774 // The branch instruction will branch to the taken block.
1775 // If taken is next, switch taken with notTaken & invert the branch condition so we can fall through.
1776 if (taken == nextBlock()) {
1777 condition = JITCompiler::invert(condition);
1778 std::swap(taken, notTaken);
1779 }
1780
1781 SpeculateBigInt32Operand op1(this, node->child1());
1782 SpeculateBigInt32Operand op2(this, node->child2());
1783 GPRReg op1GPR = op1.gpr();
1784 GPRReg op2GPR = op2.gpr();
1785
1786 if (condition == MacroAssembler::Equal || condition == MacroAssembler::NotEqual) {
1787 branch64(condition, op1GPR, op2GPR, taken);
1788 jump(notTaken);
1789 } else {
1790 GPRTemporary lhs(this, Reuse, op1);
1791 GPRTemporary rhs(this, Reuse, op2);
1792 GPRReg lhsGPR = lhs.gpr();
1793 GPRReg rhsGPR = rhs.gpr();
1794 m_jit.unboxBigInt32(op1GPR, lhsGPR);
1795 m_jit.unboxBigInt32(op2GPR, rhsGPR);
1796 branch32(condition, lhsGPR, rhsGPR, taken);
1797 jump(notTaken);
1798 }
1799
1800}
1801#endif // USE(BIGINT32)
1802
1803void SpeculativeJIT::compileCompareEqPtr(Node* node)
1804{
1805 JSValueOperand value(this, node->child1());
1806 GPRTemporary result(this);
1807 GPRReg valueGPR = value.gpr();
1808 GPRReg resultGPR = result.gpr();
1809
1810 m_jit.move(TrustedImmPtr::weakPointer(m_jit.graph(), node->cellOperand()->cell()), resultGPR);
1811 m_jit.compare64(MacroAssembler::Equal, valueGPR, resultGPR, resultGPR);
1812 unblessedBooleanResult(resultGPR, node);
1813}
1814
1815void SpeculativeJIT::compileToBooleanObjectOrOther(Edge nodeUse, bool invert)
1816{
1817 JSValueOperand value(this, nodeUse, ManualOperandSpeculation);
1818 GPRTemporary result(this);
1819 GPRReg valueGPR = value.gpr();
1820 GPRReg resultGPR = result.gpr();
1821 GPRTemporary structure;
1822 GPRReg structureGPR = InvalidGPRReg;
1823 GPRTemporary scratch;
1824 GPRReg scratchGPR = InvalidGPRReg;
1825
1826 bool masqueradesAsUndefinedWatchpointValid =
1827 masqueradesAsUndefinedWatchpointIsStillValid();
1828
1829 if (!masqueradesAsUndefinedWatchpointValid) {
1830 // The masquerades as undefined case will use the structure register, so allocate it here.
1831 // Do this at the top of the function to avoid branching around a register allocation.
1832 GPRTemporary realStructure(this);
1833 GPRTemporary realScratch(this);
1834 structure.adopt(realStructure);
1835 scratch.adopt(realScratch);
1836 structureGPR = structure.gpr();
1837 scratchGPR = scratch.gpr();
1838 }
1839
1840 MacroAssembler::Jump notCell = m_jit.branchIfNotCell(JSValueRegs(valueGPR));
1841 if (masqueradesAsUndefinedWatchpointValid) {
1842 DFG_TYPE_CHECK(
1843 JSValueRegs(valueGPR), nodeUse, (~SpecCellCheck) | SpecObject, m_jit.branchIfNotObject(valueGPR));
1844 } else {
1845 DFG_TYPE_CHECK(
1846 JSValueRegs(valueGPR), nodeUse, (~SpecCellCheck) | SpecObject, m_jit.branchIfNotObject(valueGPR));
1847
1848 MacroAssembler::Jump isNotMasqueradesAsUndefined =
1849 m_jit.branchTest8(
1850 MacroAssembler::Zero,
1851 MacroAssembler::Address(valueGPR, JSCell::typeInfoFlagsOffset()),
1852 MacroAssembler::TrustedImm32(MasqueradesAsUndefined));
1853
1854 m_jit.emitLoadStructure(vm(), valueGPR, structureGPR, scratchGPR);
1855 speculationCheck(BadType, JSValueRegs(valueGPR), nodeUse,
1856 m_jit.branchPtr(
1857 MacroAssembler::Equal,
1858 MacroAssembler::Address(structureGPR, Structure::globalObjectOffset()),
1859 TrustedImmPtr::weakPointer(m_jit.graph(), m_jit.graph().globalObjectFor(m_currentNode->origin.semantic))));
1860
1861 isNotMasqueradesAsUndefined.link(&m_jit);
1862 }
1863 m_jit.move(invert ? TrustedImm32(JSValue::ValueFalse) : TrustedImm32(JSValue::ValueTrue), resultGPR);
1864 MacroAssembler::Jump done = m_jit.jump();
1865
1866 notCell.link(&m_jit);
1867
1868 if (needsTypeCheck(nodeUse, SpecCellCheck | SpecOther)) {
1869 m_jit.move(valueGPR, resultGPR);
1870 m_jit.and64(MacroAssembler::TrustedImm32(~JSValue::UndefinedTag), resultGPR);
1871 typeCheck(
1872 JSValueRegs(valueGPR), nodeUse, SpecCellCheck | SpecOther, m_jit.branch64(
1873 MacroAssembler::NotEqual,
1874 resultGPR,
1875 MacroAssembler::TrustedImm64(JSValue::ValueNull)));
1876 }
1877 m_jit.move(invert ? TrustedImm32(JSValue::ValueTrue) : TrustedImm32(JSValue::ValueFalse), resultGPR);
1878
1879 done.link(&m_jit);
1880
1881 jsValueResult(resultGPR, m_currentNode, DataFormatJSBoolean);
1882}
1883
1884void SpeculativeJIT::compileToBoolean(Node* node, bool invert)
1885{
1886 switch (node->child1().useKind()) {
1887 case ObjectOrOtherUse: {
1888 compileToBooleanObjectOrOther(node->child1(), invert);
1889 return;
1890 }
1891
1892 case Int32Use: {
1893 SpeculateInt32Operand value(this, node->child1());
1894 GPRTemporary result(this, Reuse, value);
1895 m_jit.compare32(invert ? MacroAssembler::Equal : MacroAssembler::NotEqual, value.gpr(), MacroAssembler::TrustedImm32(0), result.gpr());
1896 m_jit.or32(TrustedImm32(JSValue::ValueFalse), result.gpr());
1897 jsValueResult(result.gpr(), node, DataFormatJSBoolean);
1898 return;
1899 }
1900
1901 case DoubleRepUse: {
1902 SpeculateDoubleOperand value(this, node->child1());
1903 FPRTemporary scratch(this);
1904 GPRTemporary result(this);
1905 m_jit.move(invert ? TrustedImm32(JSValue::ValueFalse) : TrustedImm32(JSValue::ValueTrue), result.gpr());
1906 MacroAssembler::Jump nonZero = m_jit.branchDoubleNonZero(value.fpr(), scratch.fpr());
1907 m_jit.move(invert ? TrustedImm32(JSValue::ValueTrue) : TrustedImm32(JSValue::ValueFalse), result.gpr());
1908 nonZero.link(&m_jit);
1909 jsValueResult(result.gpr(), node, DataFormatJSBoolean);
1910 return;
1911 }
1912
1913 case BooleanUse:
1914 case KnownBooleanUse: {
1915 if (!needsTypeCheck(node->child1(), SpecBoolean)) {
1916 SpeculateBooleanOperand value(this, node->child1());
1917 GPRTemporary result(this, Reuse, value);
1918
1919 if (invert)
1920 m_jit.xor32(TrustedImm32(1), value.gpr(), result.gpr());
1921 else
1922 m_jit.move(value.gpr(), result.gpr());
1923
1924 jsValueResult(result.gpr(), node, DataFormatJSBoolean);
1925 return;
1926 }
1927
1928 JSValueOperand value(this, node->child1(), ManualOperandSpeculation);
1929 GPRTemporary result(this); // FIXME: We could reuse, but on speculation fail would need recovery to restore tag (akin to add).
1930
1931 m_jit.move(value.gpr(), result.gpr());
1932 m_jit.xor64(TrustedImm32(JSValue::ValueFalse), result.gpr());
1933 typeCheck(
1934 JSValueRegs(value.gpr()), node->child1(), SpecBoolean, m_jit.branchTest64(
1935 JITCompiler::NonZero, result.gpr(), TrustedImm32(static_cast<int32_t>(~1))));
1936 m_jit.xor64(invert ? TrustedImm32(JSValue::ValueTrue) : TrustedImm32(JSValue::ValueFalse), result.gpr());
1937
1938 // If we add a DataFormatBool, we should use it here.
1939 jsValueResult(result.gpr(), node, DataFormatJSBoolean);
1940 return;
1941 }
1942
1943 case UntypedUse: {
1944 JSValueOperand arg1(this, node->child1());
1945 GPRTemporary result(this);
1946
1947 GPRReg arg1GPR = arg1.gpr();
1948 GPRReg resultGPR = result.gpr();
1949
1950 FPRTemporary valueFPR(this);
1951 FPRTemporary tempFPR(this);
1952
1953 bool shouldCheckMasqueradesAsUndefined = !masqueradesAsUndefinedWatchpointIsStillValid();
1954 JSGlobalObject* globalObject = m_jit.graph().globalObjectFor(node->origin.semantic);
1955 std::optional<GPRTemporary> scratch;
1956 GPRReg scratchGPR = InvalidGPRReg;
1957 if (shouldCheckMasqueradesAsUndefined) {
1958 scratch.emplace(this);
1959 scratchGPR = scratch->gpr();
1960 }
1961 m_jit.emitConvertValueToBoolean(vm(), JSValueRegs(arg1GPR), resultGPR, scratchGPR, valueFPR.fpr(), tempFPR.fpr(), shouldCheckMasqueradesAsUndefined, globalObject, invert);
1962 m_jit.or32(TrustedImm32(JSValue::ValueFalse), resultGPR);
1963 jsValueResult(resultGPR, node, DataFormatJSBoolean);
1964 return;
1965 }
1966 case StringUse:
1967 compileToBooleanString(node, invert);
1968 return;
1969
1970 case StringOrOtherUse:
1971 compileToBooleanStringOrOther(node, invert);
1972 return;
1973
1974 default:
1975 DFG_CRASH(m_jit.graph(), node, "Bad use kind");
1976 break;
1977 }
1978}
1979
1980void SpeculativeJIT::emitObjectOrOtherBranch(Edge nodeUse, BasicBlock* taken, BasicBlock* notTaken)
1981{
1982 JSValueOperand value(this, nodeUse, ManualOperandSpeculation);
1983 GPRTemporary scratch(this);
1984 GPRTemporary structure;
1985 GPRReg valueGPR = value.gpr();
1986 GPRReg scratchGPR = scratch.gpr();
1987 GPRReg structureGPR = InvalidGPRReg;
1988
1989 if (!masqueradesAsUndefinedWatchpointIsStillValid()) {
1990 GPRTemporary realStructure(this);
1991 structure.adopt(realStructure);
1992 structureGPR = structure.gpr();
1993 }
1994
1995 MacroAssembler::Jump notCell = m_jit.branchIfNotCell(JSValueRegs(valueGPR));
1996 if (masqueradesAsUndefinedWatchpointIsStillValid()) {
1997 DFG_TYPE_CHECK(
1998 JSValueRegs(valueGPR), nodeUse, (~SpecCellCheck) | SpecObject, m_jit.branchIfNotObject(valueGPR));
1999 } else {
2000 DFG_TYPE_CHECK(
2001 JSValueRegs(valueGPR), nodeUse, (~SpecCellCheck) | SpecObject, m_jit.branchIfNotObject(valueGPR));
2002
2003 JITCompiler::Jump isNotMasqueradesAsUndefined = m_jit.branchTest8(
2004 JITCompiler::Zero,
2005 MacroAssembler::Address(valueGPR, JSCell::typeInfoFlagsOffset()),
2006 TrustedImm32(MasqueradesAsUndefined));
2007
2008 m_jit.emitLoadStructure(vm(), valueGPR, structureGPR, scratchGPR);
2009 speculationCheck(BadType, JSValueRegs(valueGPR), nodeUse,
2010 m_jit.branchPtr(
2011 MacroAssembler::Equal,
2012 MacroAssembler::Address(structureGPR, Structure::globalObjectOffset()),
2013 TrustedImmPtr::weakPointer(m_jit.graph(), m_jit.graph().globalObjectFor(m_currentNode->origin.semantic))));
2014
2015 isNotMasqueradesAsUndefined.link(&m_jit);
2016 }
2017 jump(taken, ForceJump);
2018
2019 notCell.link(&m_jit);
2020
2021 if (needsTypeCheck(nodeUse, SpecCellCheck | SpecOther)) {
2022 m_jit.move(valueGPR, scratchGPR);
2023 m_jit.and64(MacroAssembler::TrustedImm32(~JSValue::UndefinedTag), scratchGPR);
2024 typeCheck(
2025 JSValueRegs(valueGPR), nodeUse, SpecCellCheck | SpecOther, m_jit.branch64(
2026 MacroAssembler::NotEqual, scratchGPR, MacroAssembler::TrustedImm64(JSValue::ValueNull)));
2027 }
2028 jump(notTaken);
2029
2030 noResult(m_currentNode);
2031}
2032
2033void SpeculativeJIT::emitUntypedBranch(Edge nodeUse, BasicBlock* taken, BasicBlock* notTaken)
2034{
2035 // Implements the following control flow structure, inspired by branchIfValue():
2036 // if (value is cell) {
2037 // if (value is string or value is HeapBigInt)
2038 // result = !!value->length
2039 // else {
2040 // do evil things for masquerades-as-undefined
2041 // result = true
2042 // }
2043 // } else if (value is Boolean) {
2044 // result = value == jsTrue
2045 // } else if (value is int32) {
2046 // result = !!unboxInt32(value)
2047 // } else if (value is number) {
2048 // result = !!unboxDouble(value)
2049 // } else if (value is BigInt32) {
2050 // result = !!unboxBigInt32(value)
2051 // } else {
2052 // result = false
2053 // }
2054 JSValueOperand value(this, nodeUse, ManualOperandSpeculation);
2055 GPRReg valueGPR = value.gpr();
2056 JSValueRegs valueRegs = JSValueRegs(valueGPR);
2057 GPRTemporary temp1(this);
2058 GPRTemporary temp2(this);
2059 FPRTemporary fprValue(this);
2060 FPRTemporary fprTemp(this);
2061
2062 GPRReg temp1GPR = temp1.gpr();
2063 GPRReg temp2GPR = temp2.gpr();
2064 FPRReg valueFPR = fprValue.fpr();
2065 FPRReg tempFPR = fprTemp.fpr();
2066
2067 if (needsTypeCheck(nodeUse, ~SpecCell)) {
2068 bool isDefinitelyCell = !needsTypeCheck(nodeUse, SpecCell);
2069 JITCompiler::Jump skipCellCase;
2070 if (!isDefinitelyCell)
2071 skipCellCase = m_jit.branchIfNotCell(valueRegs);
2072
2073 if (needsTypeCheck(nodeUse, ~SpecString)) {
2074 bool isDefinitelyString = !needsTypeCheck(nodeUse, SpecString | ~SpecCellCheck);
2075 JITCompiler::Jump skipStringCase;
2076 if (!isDefinitelyString)
2077 skipStringCase = m_jit.branchIfNotString(valueGPR);
2078
2079 branchPtr(MacroAssembler::Equal, valueGPR, TrustedImmPtr::weakPointer(m_jit.graph(), jsEmptyString(vm())), notTaken);
2080 jump(taken, ForceJump);
2081
2082 if (!isDefinitelyString)
2083 skipStringCase.link(&m_jit);
2084 }
2085
2086 if (needsTypeCheck(nodeUse, ~SpecHeapBigInt)) {
2087 bool isDefinitelyHeapBigInt = !needsTypeCheck(nodeUse, SpecHeapBigInt | ~SpecCellCheck);
2088 JITCompiler::Jump skipHeapBigIntCase;
2089 if (!isDefinitelyHeapBigInt)
2090 skipHeapBigIntCase = m_jit.branchIfNotHeapBigInt(valueGPR);
2091
2092 branchTest32(MacroAssembler::NonZero, MacroAssembler::Address(valueGPR, JSBigInt::offsetOfLength()), taken);
2093 jump(notTaken, ForceJump);
2094
2095 if (!isDefinitelyHeapBigInt)
2096 skipHeapBigIntCase.link(&m_jit);
2097 }
2098
2099 bool shouldCheckMasqueradesAsUndefined = !masqueradesAsUndefinedWatchpointIsStillValid();
2100 if (shouldCheckMasqueradesAsUndefined) {
2101 branchTest8(MacroAssembler::Zero, MacroAssembler::Address(valueGPR, JSCell::typeInfoFlagsOffset()), TrustedImm32(MasqueradesAsUndefined), taken);
2102 m_jit.emitLoadStructure(vm(), valueGPR, temp1GPR, temp2GPR);
2103 JSGlobalObject* globalObject = m_jit.graph().globalObjectFor(m_currentNode->origin.semantic);
2104 m_jit.move(TrustedImmPtr::weakPointer(m_jit.graph(), globalObject), temp2GPR);
2105 branchPtr(MacroAssembler::NotEqual, MacroAssembler::Address(temp1GPR, Structure::globalObjectOffset()), temp2GPR, taken);
2106 jump(notTaken, ForceJump);
2107 } else
2108 jump(taken, ForceJump);
2109
2110 if (!isDefinitelyCell)
2111 skipCellCase.link(&m_jit);
2112 }
2113
2114 if (needsTypeCheck(nodeUse, ~SpecBoolean)) {
2115 branch64(MacroAssembler::Equal, valueGPR, MacroAssembler::TrustedImm64(JSValue::encode(jsBoolean(false))), notTaken);
2116 branch64(MacroAssembler::Equal, valueGPR, MacroAssembler::TrustedImm64(JSValue::encode(jsBoolean(true))), taken);
2117 }
2118
2119 if (needsTypeCheck(nodeUse, ~SpecInt32Only)) {
2120 branch64(MacroAssembler::Above, valueGPR, GPRInfo::numberTagRegister, taken);
2121 branch64(MacroAssembler::Equal, valueGPR, GPRInfo::numberTagRegister, notTaken);
2122 }
2123
2124 if (needsTypeCheck(nodeUse, ~SpecFullDouble)) {
2125 bool isDefinitelyDouble = !needsTypeCheck(nodeUse, SpecCell | SpecBoolean | SpecInt32Only | SpecFullDouble);
2126 JITCompiler::Jump skipDoubleCase;
2127 if (!isDefinitelyDouble)
2128 skipDoubleCase = m_jit.branchIfNotNumber(valueGPR);
2129
2130 unboxDouble(valueGPR, temp1GPR, valueFPR);
2131 branchDoubleZeroOrNaN(valueFPR, tempFPR, notTaken);
2132 jump(taken, ForceJump);
2133
2134 if (!isDefinitelyDouble)
2135 skipDoubleCase.link(&m_jit);
2136 }
2137
2138#if USE(BIGINT32)
2139 if (needsTypeCheck(nodeUse, ~SpecBigInt32)) {
2140 bool isDefinitelyBigInt32 = !needsTypeCheck(nodeUse, SpecCell | SpecBoolean | SpecInt32Only | SpecFullDouble | SpecBigInt32);
2141 JITCompiler::Jump skipBigInt32Case;
2142 if (!isDefinitelyBigInt32)
2143 skipBigInt32Case = m_jit.branchIfNotBigInt32(valueGPR, tempGPR);
2144
2145 m_jit.move(valueGPR, tempGPR);
2146 m_jit.urshift64(MacroAssembler::TrustedImm32(16), tempGPR);
2147 branchTest32(MacroAssembler::NonZero, tempGPR, taken);
2148 // Here we fallthrough to the jump(notTaken) below and outside this branch.
2149
2150 if (!isDefinitelyBigInt32)
2151 skipBigInt32Case.link(&m_jit);
2152 }
2153#endif // USE(BIGINT32)
2154
2155 jump(notTaken);
2156
2157 value.use();
2158 noResult(m_currentNode, UseChildrenCalledExplicitly);
2159 return;
2160}
2161
2162void SpeculativeJIT::emitBranch(Node* node)
2163{
2164 BasicBlock* taken = node->branchData()->taken.block;
2165 BasicBlock* notTaken = node->branchData()->notTaken.block;
2166
2167 switch (node->child1().useKind()) {
2168 case ObjectOrOtherUse: {
2169 emitObjectOrOtherBranch(node->child1(), taken, notTaken);
2170 return;
2171 }
2172
2173 case Int32Use: {
2174 MacroAssembler::ResultCondition condition = MacroAssembler::NonZero;
2175
2176 if (taken == nextBlock()) {
2177 condition = MacroAssembler::Zero;
2178 BasicBlock* tmp = taken;
2179 taken = notTaken;
2180 notTaken = tmp;
2181 }
2182
2183 SpeculateInt32Operand value(this, node->child1());
2184 branchTest32(condition, value.gpr(), taken);
2185 jump(notTaken);
2186
2187 noResult(node);
2188 return;
2189 }
2190 case DoubleRepUse: {
2191 SpeculateDoubleOperand value(this, node->child1());
2192 FPRTemporary scratch(this);
2193 branchDoubleNonZero(value.fpr(), scratch.fpr(), taken);
2194 jump(notTaken);
2195
2196 noResult(node);
2197 return;
2198 }
2199
2200 case StringUse: {
2201 emitStringBranch(node->child1(), taken, notTaken);
2202 return;
2203 }
2204
2205 case StringOrOtherUse: {
2206 emitStringOrOtherBranch(node->child1(), taken, notTaken);
2207 return;
2208 }
2209
2210 case BooleanUse:
2211 case KnownBooleanUse: {
2212 JSValueOperand value(this, node->child1(), ManualOperandSpeculation);
2213 GPRReg valueGPR = value.gpr();
2214
2215 if (!needsTypeCheck(node->child1(), SpecBoolean)) {
2216 MacroAssembler::ResultCondition condition = MacroAssembler::NonZero;
2217
2218 if (taken == nextBlock()) {
2219 condition = MacroAssembler::Zero;
2220 BasicBlock* tmp = taken;
2221 taken = notTaken;
2222 notTaken = tmp;
2223 }
2224
2225 branchTest32(condition, valueGPR, TrustedImm32(true), taken);
2226 jump(notTaken);
2227 } else {
2228 branch64(MacroAssembler::Equal, valueGPR, MacroAssembler::TrustedImm64(JSValue::encode(jsBoolean(false))), notTaken);
2229 branch64(MacroAssembler::Equal, valueGPR, MacroAssembler::TrustedImm64(JSValue::encode(jsBoolean(true))), taken);
2230
2231 typeCheck(JSValueRegs(valueGPR), node->child1(), SpecBoolean, m_jit.jump());
2232 }
2233 value.use();
2234 noResult(node, UseChildrenCalledExplicitly);
2235 return;
2236 }
2237
2238 case UntypedUse: {
2239 emitUntypedBranch(node->child1(), taken, notTaken);
2240 return;
2241 }
2242
2243 default:
2244 DFG_CRASH(m_jit.graph(), m_currentNode, "Bad use kind");
2245 }
2246}
2247
2248void SpeculativeJIT::compile(Node* node)
2249{
2250 NodeType op = node->op();
2251
2252 if constexpr (validateDFGDoesGC) {
2253 if (Options::validateDoesGC()) {
2254 bool expectDoesGC = doesGC(m_jit.graph(), node);
2255 m_jit.store32(TrustedImm32(DoesGCCheck::encode(expectDoesGC, node->index(), node->op())), vm().heap.addressOfDoesGC());
2256 }
2257 }
2258
2259#if ENABLE(DFG_REGISTER_ALLOCATION_VALIDATION)

2261#endif

2263 switch (op) {
2264 case JSConstant:
2265 case DoubleConstant:

2270 break;

2286 case GetLocal: {
2287 AbstractValue& value = m_state.operand(node->operand());
2288
2289 // If the CFA is tracking this variable and it found that the variable
2290 // cannot have been assigned, then don't attempt to proceed.
2291 if (value.isClear()) {
2292 m_compileOkay = false;
2293 break;

2296 switch (node->variableAccessData()->flushFormat()) {
2297 case FlushedDouble: {
2298 FPRTemporary result(this);
2299 m_jit.loadDouble(JITCompiler::addressFor(node->machineLocal()), result.fpr());
2300 VirtualRegister virtualRegister = node->virtualRegister();
2301 m_fprs.retain(result.fpr(), virtualRegister, SpillOrderDouble);
2302 generationInfoFromVirtualRegister(virtualRegister).initDouble(node, node->refCount(), result.fpr());
2303 break;
2304 }
2305
2306 case FlushedInt32: {
2307 GPRTemporary result(this);
2308 m_jit.load32(JITCompiler::payloadFor(node->machineLocal()), result.gpr());
2309
2310 // Like strictInt32Result, but don't useChildren - our children are phi nodes,
2311 // and don't represent values within this dataflow with virtual registers.
2312 VirtualRegister virtualRegister = node->virtualRegister();
2313 m_gprs.retain(result.gpr(), virtualRegister, SpillOrderInteger);
2314 generationInfoFromVirtualRegister(virtualRegister).initInt32(node, node->refCount(), result.gpr());
2315 break;
2316 }
2317
2318 case FlushedInt52: {
2319 GPRTemporary result(this);
2320 m_jit.load64(JITCompiler::addressFor(node->machineLocal()), result.gpr());
2321
2322 VirtualRegister virtualRegister = node->virtualRegister();
2323 m_gprs.retain(result.gpr(), virtualRegister, SpillOrderJS);
2324 generationInfoFromVirtualRegister(virtualRegister).initInt52(node, node->refCount(), result.gpr());
2325 break;
2326 }
2327
2328 default:
2329 GPRTemporary result(this);
2330 m_jit.load64(JITCompiler::addressFor(node->machineLocal()), result.gpr());
2331
2332 // Like jsValueResult, but don't useChildren - our children are phi nodes,
2333 // and don't represent values within this dataflow with virtual registers.
2334 VirtualRegister virtualRegister = node->virtualRegister();
2335 m_gprs.retain(result.gpr(), virtualRegister, SpillOrderJS);
2336
2337 DataFormat format;
2338 if (isCellSpeculation(value.m_type))
2339 format = DataFormatJSCell;
2340 else if (isBooleanSpeculation(value.m_type))
2341 format = DataFormatJSBoolean;
2342 else
2343 format = DataFormatJS;
2344
2345 generationInfoFromVirtualRegister(virtualRegister).initJSValue(node, node->refCount(), result.gpr(), format);
2346 break;
2347 }
2348 break;
2349 }

2351 case MovHint: {
2352 compileMovHint(m_currentNode);
2353 noResult(node);
2354 break;
2355 }

2358 noResult(node);
2359 break;

2362 case SetLocal: {
2363 switch (node->variableAccessData()->flushFormat()) {
2364 case FlushedDouble: {
2365 SpeculateDoubleOperand value(this, node->child1());
2366 m_jit.storeDouble(value.fpr(), JITCompiler::addressFor(node->machineLocal()));
2367 noResult(node);
2368 // Indicate that it's no longer necessary to retrieve the value of
2369 // this bytecode variable from registers or other locations in the stack,
2370 // but that it is stored as a double.
2371 recordSetLocal(DataFormatDouble);
2372 break;
2373 }
2374
2375 case FlushedInt32: {
2376 SpeculateInt32Operand value(this, node->child1());
2377 m_jit.store32(value.gpr(), JITCompiler::payloadFor(node->machineLocal()));
2378 noResult(node);
2379 recordSetLocal(DataFormatInt32);
2380 break;
2381 }

2383 case FlushedInt52: {
2384 SpeculateInt52Operand value(this, node->child1());
2385 m_jit.store64(value.gpr(), JITCompiler::addressFor(node->machineLocal()));
2386 noResult(node);
2387 recordSetLocal(DataFormatInt52);
2388 break;
2389 }

2391 case FlushedCell: {
2392 SpeculateCellOperand cell(this, node->child1());
2393 GPRReg cellGPR = cell.gpr();
2394 m_jit.store64(cellGPR, JITCompiler::addressFor(node->machineLocal()));
2395 noResult(node);
2396 recordSetLocal(DataFormatCell);
2397 break;
2398 }
2399
2400 case FlushedBoolean: {
2401 SpeculateBooleanOperand boolean(this, node->child1());
2402 m_jit.store64(boolean.gpr(), JITCompiler::addressFor(node->machineLocal()));
2403 noResult(node);
2404 recordSetLocal(DataFormatBoolean);
2405 break;
2406 }
2407
2408 case FlushedJSValue: {
2409 JSValueOperand value(this, node->child1());
2410 m_jit.store64(value.gpr(), JITCompiler::addressFor(node->machineLocal()));
2411 noResult(node);
2412 recordSetLocal(dataFormatFor(node->variableAccessData()->flushFormat()));
2413 break;
2414 }
2415
2416 default:
2417 DFG_CRASH(m_jit.graph(), node, "Bad flush format");
2418 break;
2419 }
2420
2421 break;

2524 JSValueRegs(), node->child1(), SpecAnyIntAsDouble,

2526 JITCompiler::Equal, resultGPR,

2747 case GetByVal: {
2748 switch (node->arrayMode().type()) {
2749 case Array::AnyTypedArray:
2750 case Array::ForceExit:
2751 case Array::SelectUsingArguments:
2752 case Array::SelectUsingPredictions:
2753 case Array::Unprofiled:
2754 DFG_CRASH(m_jit.graph(), node, "Bad array mode type");
2755 break;
2756 case Array::Undecided: {
2757 SpeculateStrictInt32Operand index(this, m_graph.varArgChild(node, 1));
2758 GPRTemporary result(this, Reuse, index);
2759 GPRReg indexGPR = index.gpr();
2760 GPRReg resultGPR = result.gpr();
2761
2762 speculationCheck(OutOfBounds, JSValueRegs(), node,
2763 m_jit.branch32(MacroAssembler::LessThan, indexGPR, MacroAssembler::TrustedImm32(0)));
2764
2765 use(m_graph.varArgChild(node, 0));
2766 index.use();
2767
2768 m_jit.move(MacroAssembler::TrustedImm64(JSValue::ValueUndefined), resultGPR);
2769 jsValueResult(resultGPR, node, UseChildrenCalledExplicitly);
2770 break;
2771 }
2772 case Array::BigInt64Array:
2773 case Array::BigUint64Array:
2774 case Array::Generic: {
2775 if (m_graph.m_slowGetByVal.contains(node)) {
2776 if (m_graph.varArgChild(node, 0).useKind() == ObjectUse) {
2777 if (m_graph.varArgChild(node, 1).useKind() == StringUse) {
2778 compileGetByValForObjectWithString(node);
2779 break;
2780 }
2781
2782 if (m_graph.varArgChild(node, 1).useKind() == SymbolUse) {
2783 compileGetByValForObjectWithSymbol(node);
2784 break;
2785 }
2786 }
2787
2788 JSValueOperand base(this, m_graph.varArgChild(node, 0));
2789 JSValueOperand property(this, m_graph.varArgChild(node, 1));
2790 GPRReg baseGPR = base.gpr();
2791 GPRReg propertyGPR = property.gpr();
2792
2793 flushRegisters();
2794 GPRFlushedCallResult result(this);
2795 callOperation(operationGetByVal, result.gpr(), TrustedImmPtr::weakPointer(m_graph, m_graph.globalObjectFor(node->origin.semantic)), baseGPR, propertyGPR);
2796 m_jit.exceptionCheck();
2797
2798 jsValueResult(result.gpr(), node);
2799 break;
2800 }
2801
2802 std::optional<GPRTemporary> stubInfo;
2803 JSValueOperand base(this, m_graph.varArgChild(node, 0), ManualOperandSpeculation);
2804 JSValueOperand property(this, m_graph.varArgChild(node, 1), ManualOperandSpeculation);
2805 GPRTemporary result(this, Reuse, property);
2806
2807 GPRReg stubInfoGPR = InvalidGPRReg;
2808 if (JITCode::useDataIC(JITType::DFGJIT)) {
2809 stubInfo.emplace(this);
2810 stubInfoGPR = stubInfo->gpr();
2811 }
2812 GPRReg baseGPR = base.gpr();
2813 GPRReg propertyGPR = property.gpr();
2814 GPRReg resultGPR = result.gpr();
2815
2816 speculate(node, m_graph.varArgChild(node, 0));
2817 speculate(node, m_graph.varArgChild(node, 1));
2818
2819 CodeOrigin codeOrigin = node->origin.semantic;
2820 CallSiteIndex callSite = m_jit.recordCallSiteAndGenerateExceptionHandlingOSRExitIfNeeded(codeOrigin, m_stream->size());
2821 RegisterSet usedRegisters = this->usedRegisters();
2822
2823 JITCompiler::JumpList slowCases;
2824 if (!m_state.forNode(m_graph.varArgChild(node, 0)).isType(SpecCell))
2825 slowCases.append(m_jit.branchIfNotCell(baseGPR));
2826
2827 JITGetByValGenerator gen(
2828 m_jit.codeBlock(), JITType::DFGJIT, codeOrigin, callSite, AccessType::GetByVal, usedRegisters,
2829 JSValueRegs(baseGPR), JSValueRegs(propertyGPR), JSValueRegs(resultGPR), stubInfoGPR);
2830
2831 if (m_state.forNode(m_graph.varArgChild(node, 1)).isType(SpecString))
2832 gen.stubInfo()->propertyIsString = true;
2833 else if (m_state.forNode(m_graph.varArgChild(node, 1)).isType(SpecInt32Only))
2834 gen.stubInfo()->propertyIsInt32 = true;
2835 else if (m_state.forNode(m_graph.varArgChild(node, 1)).isType(SpecSymbol))
2836 gen.stubInfo()->propertyIsSymbol = true;
2837
2838 gen.generateFastPath(m_jit);
2839
2840 if (!JITCode::useDataIC(JITType::DFGJIT))
2841 slowCases.append(gen.slowPathJump());
2842
2843 std::unique_ptr<SlowPathGenerator> slowPath;
2844 if (JITCode::useDataIC(JITType::DFGJIT)) {
2845 slowPath = slowPathICCall(
2846 slowCases, this, gen.stubInfo(), stubInfoGPR, CCallHelpers::Address(stubInfoGPR, StructureStubInfo::offsetOfSlowOperation()), operationGetByValOptimize,
2847 resultGPR, TrustedImmPtr::weakPointer(m_graph, m_graph.globalObjectFor(codeOrigin)), stubInfoGPR, nullptr, baseGPR, propertyGPR);
2848 } else {
2849 slowPath = slowPathCall(
2850 slowCases, this, operationGetByValOptimize,
2851 resultGPR, TrustedImmPtr::weakPointer(m_graph, m_graph.globalObjectFor(codeOrigin)), gen.stubInfo(), nullptr, baseGPR, propertyGPR);
2852 }
2853
2854 m_jit.addGetByVal(gen, slowPath.get());
2855 addSlowPathGenerator(WTFMove(slowPath));
2856
2857 jsValueResult(resultGPR, node);
2858 break;
2859 }
2860 case Array::Int32:
2861 case Array::Contiguous: {
2862 if (node->arrayMode().isInBounds()) {
2863 SpeculateStrictInt32Operand property(this, m_graph.varArgChild(node, 1));
2864 StorageOperand storage(this, m_graph.varArgChild(node, 2));
2865
2866 GPRReg propertyReg = property.gpr();
2867 GPRReg storageReg = storage.gpr();
2868
2869 if (!m_compileOkay)
2870 return;
2871
2872 speculationCheck(OutOfBounds, JSValueRegs(), nullptr, m_jit.branch32(MacroAssembler::AboveOrEqual, propertyReg, MacroAssembler::Address(storageReg, Butterfly::offsetOfPublicLength())));
2873
2874 GPRTemporary result(this);
2875
2876 m_jit.load64(MacroAssembler::BaseIndex(storageReg, propertyReg, MacroAssembler::TimesEight), result.gpr());
2877 if (node->arrayMode().isInBoundsSaneChain()) {
2878 ASSERT(node->arrayMode().type() == Array::Contiguous);
2879 JITCompiler::Jump notHole = m_jit.branchIfNotEmpty(result.gpr());
2880 m_jit.move(TrustedImm64(JSValue::encode(jsUndefined())), result.gpr());
2881 notHole.link(&m_jit);
2882 } else {
2883 speculationCheck(
2884 LoadFromHole, JSValueRegs(), nullptr,
2885 m_jit.branchIfEmpty(result.gpr()));
2886 }
2887 jsValueResult(result.gpr(), node, node->arrayMode().type() == Array::Int32 ? DataFormatJSInt32 : DataFormatJS);
2888 break;
2889 }
2890
2891 SpeculateCellOperand base(this, m_graph.varArgChild(node, 0));
2892 SpeculateStrictInt32Operand property(this, m_graph.varArgChild(node, 1));
2893 StorageOperand storage(this, m_graph.varArgChild(node, 2));
2894
2895 GPRReg baseReg = base.gpr();
2896 GPRReg propertyReg = property.gpr();
2897 GPRReg storageReg = storage.gpr();
2898
2899 if (!m_compileOkay)
2900 return;
2901
2902 GPRTemporary result(this);
2903 GPRReg resultReg = result.gpr();
2904
2905 MacroAssembler::JumpList slowCases;
2906
2907 slowCases.append(m_jit.branch32(MacroAssembler::AboveOrEqual, propertyReg, MacroAssembler::Address(storageReg, Butterfly::offsetOfPublicLength())));
2908
2909 m_jit.load64(MacroAssembler::BaseIndex(storageReg, propertyReg, MacroAssembler::TimesEight), resultReg);
2910
2911 if (node->arrayMode().isOutOfBoundsSaneChain()) {
2912 auto done = m_jit.branchIfNotEmpty(resultReg);
2913 slowCases.link(&m_jit);
2914 speculationCheck(NegativeIndex, JSValueRegs(), nullptr, m_jit.branch32(MacroAssembler::LessThan, propertyReg, CCallHelpers::TrustedImm32(0)));
2915 m_jit.move(CCallHelpers::TrustedImm64(JSValue::encode(jsUndefined())), resultReg);
2916 done.link(&m_jit);
2917 } else {
2918 slowCases.append(m_jit.branchIfEmpty(resultReg));
2919 addSlowPathGenerator(
2920 slowPathCall(
2921 slowCases, this, operationGetByValObjectInt,
2922 result.gpr(), TrustedImmPtr::weakPointer(m_graph, m_graph.globalObjectFor(node->origin.semantic)), baseReg, propertyReg));
2923 }
2924
2925
2926 jsValueResult(resultReg, node);
2927 break;
2928 }
2929
2930 case Array::Double: {
2931 if (node->arrayMode().isInBounds()) {
2932 SpeculateStrictInt32Operand property(this, m_graph.varArgChild(node, 1));
2933 StorageOperand storage(this, m_graph.varArgChild(node, 2));
2934
2935 GPRReg propertyReg = property.gpr();
2936 GPRReg storageReg = storage.gpr();
2937
2938 if (!m_compileOkay)
2939 return;
2940
2941 FPRTemporary result(this);
2942 FPRReg resultReg = result.fpr();
2943
2944 speculationCheck(OutOfBounds, JSValueRegs(), nullptr, m_jit.branch32(MacroAssembler::AboveOrEqual, propertyReg, MacroAssembler::Address(storageReg, Butterfly::offsetOfPublicLength())));
2945
2946 m_jit.loadDouble(MacroAssembler::BaseIndex(storageReg, propertyReg, MacroAssembler::TimesEight), resultReg);
2947 if (!node->arrayMode().isInBoundsSaneChain())
2948 speculationCheck(LoadFromHole, JSValueRegs(), nullptr, m_jit.branchIfNaN(resultReg));
2949 doubleResult(resultReg, node);
2950 break;
2951 }
2952
2953 bool resultIsUnboxed = node->arrayMode().isOutOfBoundsSaneChain() && !(node->flags() & NodeBytecodeUsesAsOther);
2954
2955 SpeculateCellOperand base(this, m_graph.varArgChild(node, 0));
2956 SpeculateStrictInt32Operand property(this, m_graph.varArgChild(node, 1));
2957 StorageOperand storage(this, m_graph.varArgChild(node, 2));
2958
2959 GPRReg baseReg = base.gpr();
2960 GPRReg propertyReg = property.gpr();
2961 GPRReg storageReg = storage.gpr();
2962
2963 if (!m_compileOkay)
2964 return;
2965
2966 std::optional<GPRTemporary> result;
2967 std::optional<GPRReg> resultReg;
2968 if (!resultIsUnboxed) {
2969 result.emplace(this);
2970 resultReg = result->gpr();

3572 break;
3573 case Int52RepUse:
3574 strictInt52Result(resultGPR, node);
3575 break;
3576 default:
3577 DFG_CRASH(m_graph, node, "Bad result type");
3578 break;
3579 }
3580 break;
3581 }
3582 constexpr bool canSpeculate = false;
3583 setIntTypedArrayLoadResult(node, resultGPR, type, canSpeculate);
3584 break;
3585 }

3587 case AtomicsIsLockFree: {
3588 Edge child1 = m_graph.child(node, 0);
3589 if (child1.useKind() != Int32Use) {
3590 JSValueOperand operand(this, child1);
3591 GPRReg operandGPR = operand.gpr();
3592 flushRegisters();
3593 GPRFlushedCallResult result(this);
3594 GPRReg resultGPR = result.gpr();
3595 callOperation(operationAtomicsIsLockFree, resultGPR, TrustedImmPtr::weakPointer(m_graph, m_graph.globalObjectFor(node->origin.semantic)), operandGPR);
3596 m_jit.exceptionCheck();
3597 jsValueResult(resultGPR, node);
3598 break;
3599 }
3600
3601 SpeculateInt32Operand operand(this, child1);
3602 GPRTemporary result(this);
3603 GPRReg operandGPR = operand.gpr();
3604 GPRReg resultGPR = result.gpr();
3605 m_jit.move(TrustedImm32(JSValue::ValueTrue), resultGPR);
3606 JITCompiler::JumpList done;
3607 done.append(m_jit.branch32(JITCompiler::Equal, operandGPR, TrustedImm32(8)));
3608 done.append(m_jit.branch32(JITCompiler::Equal, operandGPR, TrustedImm32(4)));
3609 done.append(m_jit.branch32(JITCompiler::Equal, operandGPR, TrustedImm32(1)));
3610 done.append(m_jit.branch32(JITCompiler::Equal, operandGPR, TrustedImm32(2)));
3611 m_jit.move(TrustedImm32(JSValue::ValueFalse), resultGPR);
3612 done.link(&m_jit);
3613 jsValueResult(resultGPR, node);
3614 break;

3678 case ArrayPop: {
3679 ASSERT(node->arrayMode().isJSArray());
3680
3681 SpeculateCellOperand base(this, node->child1());
3682 StorageOperand storage(this, node->child2());
3683 GPRTemporary value(this);
3684 GPRTemporary storageLength(this);
3685 FPRTemporary temp(this); // This is kind of lame, since we don't always need it. I'm relying on the fact that we don't have FPR pressure, especially in code that uses pop().
3686
3687 GPRReg baseGPR = base.gpr();
3688 GPRReg storageGPR = storage.gpr();
3689 GPRReg valueGPR = value.gpr();
3690 GPRReg storageLengthGPR = storageLength.gpr();
3691 FPRReg tempFPR = temp.fpr();
3692
3693 switch (node->arrayMode().type()) {
3694 case Array::Int32:
3695 case Array::Double:
3696 case Array::Contiguous: {
3697 m_jit.load32(
3698 MacroAssembler::Address(storageGPR, Butterfly::offsetOfPublicLength()), storageLengthGPR);
3699 MacroAssembler::Jump undefinedCase =
3700 m_jit.branchTest32(MacroAssembler::Zero, storageLengthGPR);
3701 m_jit.sub32(TrustedImm32(1), storageLengthGPR);
3702 m_jit.store32(
3703 storageLengthGPR, MacroAssembler::Address(storageGPR, Butterfly::offsetOfPublicLength()));
3704 MacroAssembler::Jump slowCase;
3705 if (node->arrayMode().type() == Array::Double) {
3706 m_jit.loadDouble(
3707 MacroAssembler::BaseIndex(storageGPR, storageLengthGPR, MacroAssembler::TimesEight),
3708 tempFPR);
3709 // FIXME: This would not have to be here if changing the publicLength also zeroed the values between the old
3710 // length and the new length.
3711 m_jit.store64(
3712 MacroAssembler::TrustedImm64(bitwise_cast<int64_t>(PNaN)), MacroAssembler::BaseIndex(storageGPR, storageLengthGPR, MacroAssembler::TimesEight));
3713 slowCase = m_jit.branchIfNaN(tempFPR);
3714 boxDouble(tempFPR, valueGPR);
3715 } else {
3716 m_jit.load64(
3717 MacroAssembler::BaseIndex(storageGPR, storageLengthGPR, MacroAssembler::TimesEight),
3718 valueGPR);
3719 // FIXME: This would not have to be here if changing the publicLength also zeroed the values between the old
3720 // length and the new length.
3721 m_jit.store64(
3722 MacroAssembler::TrustedImm64((int64_t)0), MacroAssembler::BaseIndex(storageGPR, storageLengthGPR, MacroAssembler::TimesEight));
3723 slowCase = m_jit.branchIfEmpty(valueGPR);
3724 }
3725
3726 addSlowPathGenerator(
3727 slowPathMove(
3728 undefinedCase, this,
3729 MacroAssembler::TrustedImm64(JSValue::encode(jsUndefined())), valueGPR));
3730 addSlowPathGenerator(
3731 slowPathCall(
3732 slowCase, this, operationArrayPopAndRecoverLength, valueGPR, TrustedImmPtr::weakPointer(m_graph, m_graph.globalObjectFor(node->origin.semantic)), baseGPR));
3733
3734 // We can't know for sure that the result is an int because of the slow paths. :-/
3735 jsValueResult(valueGPR, node);
3736 break;
3737 }
3738
3739 case Array::ArrayStorage: {
3740 m_jit.load32(MacroAssembler::Address(storageGPR, ArrayStorage::lengthOffset()), storageLengthGPR);
3741
3742 JITCompiler::Jump undefinedCase =
3743 m_jit.branchTest32(MacroAssembler::Zero, storageLengthGPR);
3744
3745 m_jit.sub32(TrustedImm32(1), storageLengthGPR);
3746
3747 JITCompiler::JumpList slowCases;
3748 slowCases.append(m_jit.branch32(MacroAssembler::AboveOrEqual, storageLengthGPR, MacroAssembler::Address(storageGPR, ArrayStorage::vectorLengthOffset())));
3749
3750 m_jit.load64(MacroAssembler::BaseIndex(storageGPR, storageLengthGPR, MacroAssembler::TimesEight, ArrayStorage::vectorOffset()), valueGPR);
3751 slowCases.append(m_jit.branchIfEmpty(valueGPR));
3752
3753 m_jit.store32(storageLengthGPR, MacroAssembler::Address(storageGPR, ArrayStorage::lengthOffset()));
3754
3755 m_jit.store64(MacroAssembler::TrustedImm64((int64_t)0), MacroAssembler::BaseIndex(storageGPR, storageLengthGPR, MacroAssembler::TimesEight, ArrayStorage::vectorOffset()));
3756 m_jit.sub32(MacroAssembler::TrustedImm32(1), MacroAssembler::Address(storageGPR, OBJECT_OFFSETOF(ArrayStorage, m_numValuesInVector)));
3757
3758 addSlowPathGenerator(
3759 slowPathMove(
3760 undefinedCase, this,
3761 MacroAssembler::TrustedImm64(JSValue::encode(jsUndefined())), valueGPR));
3762
3763 addSlowPathGenerator(
3764 slowPathCall(
3765 slowCases, this, operationArrayPop, valueGPR, TrustedImmPtr::weakPointer(m_graph, m_graph.globalObjectFor(node->origin.semantic)), baseGPR));
3766
3767 jsValueResult(valueGPR, node);
3768 break;
3769 }
3770
3771 default:
3772 CRASH();
3773 break;
3774 }
3775 break;
3776 }

3824
3825 m_jit.move(value.gpr(), result.gpr());
3826 m_jit.xor64(TrustedImm32(JSValue::ValueFalse), result.gpr());
3827 DFG_TYPE_CHECK(
3828 JSValueRegs(value.gpr()), node->child1(), SpecBoolean, m_jit.branchTest64(
3829 JITCompiler::NonZero, result.gpr(), TrustedImm32(static_cast<int32_t>(~1))));

3842 strictInt32Result(result.gpr(), node);

3847 m_jit.xor64(TrustedImm32(JSValue::ValueFalse), result.gpr());
3848 JITCompiler::Jump isBoolean = m_jit.branchTest64(
3849 JITCompiler::Zero, result.gpr(), TrustedImm32(static_cast<int32_t>(~1)));
3850 m_jit.move(value.gpr(), result.gpr());
3851 JITCompiler::Jump done = m_jit.jump();
3852 isBoolean.link(&m_jit);
3853 m_jit.or64(GPRInfo::numberTagRegister, result.gpr());
3854 done.link(&m_jit);

3901 silentFillAllRegisters();

3903
3904 done.link(&m_jit);
3905 }

4585 JSValueRegs valueRegs = JSValueRegs(value.gpr());
4586 GPRReg resultGPR = result.gpr();

4588 FPRReg tempFPR1 = temp1.fpr();
4589 FPRReg tempFPR2 = temp2.fpr();

4593 auto isInt32 = m_jit.branchIfInt32(valueRegs);
4594 auto notNumber = m_jit.branchIfNotDoubleKnownNotInt32(valueRegs);

4597 m_jit.unboxDouble(valueRegs.gpr(), resultGPR, tempFPR1);
4598 m_jit.urshift64(TrustedImm32(52), resultGPR);
4599 m_jit.and32(TrustedImm32(0x7ff), resultGPR);
4600 auto notNanNorInfinity = m_jit.branch32(JITCompiler::NotEqual, TrustedImm32(0x7ff), resultGPR);
4601 m_jit.move(TrustedImm32(JSValue::ValueFalse), resultGPR);
4602 done.append(m_jit.jump());
4603
4604 notNanNorInfinity.link(&m_jit);
4605 m_jit.roundTowardZeroDouble(tempFPR1, tempFPR2);
4606 m_jit.compareDouble(JITCompiler::DoubleEqualAndOrdered, tempFPR1, tempFPR2, resultGPR);
4607 m_jit.or32(TrustedImm32(JSValue::ValueFalse), resultGPR);
4608 done.append(m_jit.jump());
4609
4610 isInt32.link(&m_jit);

4612 done.append(m_jit.jump());
4613
4614 notNumber.link(&m_jit);
4615 m_jit.move(TrustedImm32(JSValue::ValueFalse), resultGPR);

4622 case MapHash: {

4628 case Int32Use:

4659 case CellUse:
4660 case StringUse: {

4662 GPRTemporary result(this);
4663 std::optional<GPRTemporary> temp;
4664

4666 if (node->child1().useKind() == CellUse) {
4667 temp.emplace(this);
4668 tempGPR = temp->gpr();

4672 GPRReg resultGPR = result.gpr();
4673
4674 MacroAssembler::JumpList slowPath;
4675 MacroAssembler::JumpList done;
4676
4677 if (node->child1().useKind() == StringUse)
4678 speculateString(node->child1(), inputGPR);
4679 else {
4680 auto isString = m_jit.branchIfString(inputGPR);
4681 auto isHeapBigInt = m_jit.branchIfHeapBigInt(inputGPR);
4682 m_jit.move(inputGPR, resultGPR);
4683 m_jit.wangsInt64Hash(resultGPR, tempGPR);
4684 addSlowPathGenerator(slowPathCall(isHeapBigInt, this, operationMapHashHeapBigInt, NeedToSpill, ExceptionCheckRequirement::CheckNotNeeded, resultGPR, &vm(), inputGPR));
4685 done.append(m_jit.jump());
4686 isString.link(&m_jit);

4690 slowPath.append(m_jit.branchIfRopeStringImpl(resultGPR));
4691 m_jit.load32(MacroAssembler::Address(resultGPR, StringImpl::flagsOffset()), resultGPR);
4692 m_jit.urshift32(MacroAssembler::TrustedImm32(StringImpl::s_flagCount), resultGPR);
4693 slowPath.append(m_jit.branchTest32(MacroAssembler::Zero, resultGPR));
4694 done.append(m_jit.jump());
4695
4696 slowPath.link(&m_jit);
4697 silentSpillAllRegisters(resultGPR);
4698 callOperation(operationMapHash, resultGPR, TrustedImmPtr::weakPointer(m_graph, m_graph.globalObjectFor(node->origin.semantic)), JSValueRegs(inputGPR));
4699 silentFillAllRegisters();
4700 m_jit.exceptionCheck();
4701
4702 done.link(&m_jit);
4703 strictInt32Result(resultGPR, node);
4704 break;
4705 }
4706 default:
4707 RELEASE_ASSERT(node->child1().useKind() == UntypedUse);
4708 break;
4709 }
4710
4711 if (node->child1().useKind() != UntypedUse)
4712 break;
4713
4714 JSValueOperand input(this, node->child1());
4715 GPRTemporary temp(this);
4716 GPRTemporary result(this);
4717
4718 GPRReg inputGPR = input.gpr();
4719 GPRReg resultGPR = result.gpr();
4720 GPRReg tempGPR = temp.gpr();
4721
4722 MacroAssembler::JumpList straightHash;
4723 MacroAssembler::JumpList done;
4724 straightHash.append(m_jit.branchIfNotCell(inputGPR));
4725 MacroAssembler::JumpList slowPath;
4726 auto isHeapBigInt = m_jit.branchIfHeapBigInt(inputGPR);
4727 straightHash.append(m_jit.branchIfNotString(inputGPR));
4728 m_jit.loadPtr(MacroAssembler::Address(inputGPR, JSString::offsetOfValue()), resultGPR);
4729 slowPath.append(m_jit.branchIfRopeStringImpl(resultGPR));
4730 m_jit.load32(MacroAssembler::Address(resultGPR, StringImpl::flagsOffset()), resultGPR);
4731 m_jit.urshift32(MacroAssembler::TrustedImm32(StringImpl::s_flagCount), resultGPR);
4732 slowPath.append(m_jit.branchTest32(MacroAssembler::Zero, resultGPR));
4733 done.append(m_jit.jump());
4734
4735 straightHash.link(&m_jit);
4736 m_jit.move(inputGPR, resultGPR);
4737 m_jit.wangsInt64Hash(resultGPR, tempGPR);
4738 addSlowPathGenerator(slowPathCall(isHeapBigInt, this, operationMapHashHeapBigInt, NeedToSpill, ExceptionCheckRequirement::CheckNotNeeded, resultGPR, &vm(), inputGPR));
4739 done.append(m_jit.jump());
4740
4741 slowPath.link(&m_jit);
4742 silentSpillAllRegisters(resultGPR);
4743 callOperation(operationMapHash, resultGPR, TrustedImmPtr::weakPointer(m_graph, m_graph.globalObjectFor(node->origin.semantic)), JSValueRegs(inputGPR));
4744 silentFillAllRegisters();
4745 m_jit.exceptionCheck();

4747 done.link(&m_jit);

4756
4757 case GetMapBucket: {
4758 SpeculateCellOperand map(this, node->child1());
4759 JSValueOperand key(this, node->child2(), ManualOperandSpeculation);
4760 SpeculateInt32Operand hash(this, node->child3());
4761 GPRTemporary mask(this);
4762 GPRTemporary index(this);
4763 GPRTemporary buffer(this);
4764 GPRTemporary bucket(this);
4765 GPRTemporary result(this);
4766
4767 GPRReg hashGPR = hash.gpr();
4768 GPRReg mapGPR = map.gpr();
4769 GPRReg maskGPR = mask.gpr();
4770 GPRReg indexGPR = index.gpr();
4771 GPRReg bufferGPR = buffer.gpr();
4772 GPRReg bucketGPR = bucket.gpr();
4773 GPRReg keyGPR = key.gpr();
4774 GPRReg resultGPR = result.gpr();
4775
4776 if (node->child1().useKind() == MapObjectUse)
4777 speculateMapObject(node->child1(), mapGPR);
4778 else if (node->child1().useKind() == SetObjectUse)
4779 speculateSetObject(node->child1(), mapGPR);
4780 else
4781 RELEASE_ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
4782
4783 if (node->child2().useKind() != UntypedUse)
4784 speculate(node, node->child2());
4785
4786 m_jit.load32(MacroAssembler::Address(mapGPR, HashMapImpl<HashMapBucket<HashMapBucketDataKey>>::offsetOfCapacity()), maskGPR);
4787 m_jit.loadPtr(MacroAssembler::Address(mapGPR, HashMapImpl<HashMapBucket<HashMapBucketDataKey>>::offsetOfBuffer()), bufferGPR);
4788 m_jit.sub32(TrustedImm32(1), maskGPR);
4789 m_jit.move(hashGPR, indexGPR);
4790
4791 MacroAssembler::Label loop = m_jit.label();
4792 MacroAssembler::JumpList done;
4793 MacroAssembler::JumpList slowPathCases;
4794 MacroAssembler::JumpList loopAround;
4795
4796 m_jit.and32(maskGPR, indexGPR);
4797 m_jit.loadPtr(MacroAssembler::BaseIndex(bufferGPR, indexGPR, MacroAssembler::TimesEight), bucketGPR);
4798 m_jit.move(bucketGPR, resultGPR);
4799 auto notPresentInTable = m_jit.branchPtr(MacroAssembler::Equal,
4800 bucketGPR, TrustedImmPtr(bitwise_cast<size_t>(HashMapImpl<HashMapBucket<HashMapBucketDataKey>>::emptyValue())));
4801 loopAround.append(m_jit.branchPtr(MacroAssembler::Equal,
4802 bucketGPR, TrustedImmPtr(bitwise_cast<size_t>(HashMapImpl<HashMapBucket<HashMapBucketDataKey>>::deletedValue()))));
4803
4804 m_jit.load64(MacroAssembler::Address(bucketGPR, HashMapBucket<HashMapBucketDataKey>::offsetOfKey()), bucketGPR);
4805
4806 // Perform Object.is()
4807 switch (node->child2().useKind()) {
4808 case BooleanUse:
4809#if USE(BIGINT32)
4810 case BigInt32Use:
4811#endif
4812 case Int32Use:
4813 case SymbolUse:
4814 case ObjectUse: {
4815 done.append(m_jit.branch64(MacroAssembler::Equal, bucketGPR, keyGPR)); // They're definitely the same value, we found the bucket we were looking for!
4816 // Otherwise, loop around.
4817 break;
4818 }
4819 case CellUse: {
4820 // if (bucket.isString()) {
4821 // if (key.isString())
4822 // => slow path
4823 // } else if (bucket.isHeapBigInt()) {
4824 // if (key.isHeapBigInt())
4825 // => slow path
4826 // }
4827 done.append(m_jit.branch64(MacroAssembler::Equal, bucketGPR, keyGPR));
4828 loopAround.append(m_jit.branchIfNotCell(JSValueRegs(bucketGPR)));
4829
4830 auto bucketIsString = m_jit.branchIfString(bucketGPR);
4831 loopAround.append(m_jit.branchIfNotHeapBigInt(bucketGPR));
4832
4833 // bucket is HeapBigInt.
4834 slowPathCases.append(m_jit.branchIfHeapBigInt(keyGPR));
4835 loopAround.append(m_jit.jump());
4836
4837 // bucket is String.
4838 bucketIsString.link(&m_jit);
4839 loopAround.append(m_jit.branchIfNotString(keyGPR));
4840 slowPathCases.append(m_jit.jump());
4841 break;
4842 }
4843 case StringUse: {
4844 done.append(m_jit.branch64(MacroAssembler::Equal, bucketGPR, keyGPR)); // They're definitely the same value, we found the bucket we were looking for!
4845 loopAround.append(m_jit.branchIfNotCell(JSValueRegs(bucketGPR)));
4846 loopAround.append(m_jit.branchIfNotString(bucketGPR));
4847 slowPathCases.append(m_jit.jump());
4848 break;
4849 }
4850 case HeapBigIntUse: {
4851 done.append(m_jit.branch64(MacroAssembler::Equal, bucketGPR, keyGPR)); // They're definitely the same value, we found the bucket we were looking for!
4852 loopAround.append(m_jit.branchIfNotCell(JSValueRegs(bucketGPR)));
4853 loopAround.append(m_jit.branchIfNotHeapBigInt(bucketGPR));
4854 slowPathCases.append(m_jit.jump());
4855 break;
4856 }
4857 case UntypedUse: {
4858 done.append(m_jit.branch64(MacroAssembler::Equal, bucketGPR, keyGPR)); // They're definitely the same value, we found the bucket we were looking for!
4859 // The input key and bucket's key are already normalized. So if 64-bit compare fails and one is not a cell, they're definitely not equal.
4860 loopAround.append(m_jit.branchIfNotCell(JSValueRegs(bucketGPR)));
4861 // first is a cell here.
4862 loopAround.append(m_jit.branchIfNotCell(JSValueRegs(keyGPR)));
4863 // Both are cells here.
4864 auto bucketIsString = m_jit.branchIfString(bucketGPR);
4865 // bucket is not String.
4866 loopAround.append(m_jit.branchIfNotHeapBigInt(bucketGPR));
4867 // bucket is HeapBigInt.
4868 slowPathCases.append(m_jit.branchIfHeapBigInt(keyGPR));
4869 loopAround.append(m_jit.jump());
4870 // bucket is String.
4871 bucketIsString.link(&m_jit);
4872 loopAround.append(m_jit.branchIfNotString(keyGPR));
4873 slowPathCases.append(m_jit.jump());
4874 break;
4875 }
4876 default:
4877 RELEASE_ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
4878 }
4879
4880
4881 if (!loopAround.empty())
4882 loopAround.link(&m_jit);
4883
4884 m_jit.add32(TrustedImm32(1), indexGPR);
4885 m_jit.jump().linkTo(loop, &m_jit);
4886
4887 if (!slowPathCases.empty()) {
4888 slowPathCases.link(&m_jit);
4889 silentSpillAllRegisters(indexGPR);
4890 if (node->child1().useKind() == MapObjectUse)
4891 callOperation(operationJSMapFindBucket, resultGPR, TrustedImmPtr::weakPointer(m_graph, m_graph.globalObjectFor(node->origin.semantic)), mapGPR, keyGPR, hashGPR);
4892 else
4893 callOperation(operationJSSetFindBucket, resultGPR, TrustedImmPtr::weakPointer(m_graph, m_graph.globalObjectFor(node->origin.semantic)), mapGPR, keyGPR, hashGPR);
4894 silentFillAllRegisters();
4895 m_jit.exceptionCheck();
4896 done.append(m_jit.jump());
4897 }
4898
4899 notPresentInTable.link(&m_jit);
4900 if (node->child1().useKind() == MapObjectUse)
4901 m_jit.move(TrustedImmPtr::weakPointer(m_jit.graph(), vm().sentinelMapBucket()), resultGPR);
4902 else
4903 m_jit.move(TrustedImmPtr::weakPointer(m_jit.graph(), vm().sentinelSetBucket()), resultGPR);
4904 done.link(&m_jit);
4905 cellResult(resultGPR, node);
4906 break;
4907 }
4908
4909 case GetMapBucketHead:
4910 compileGetMapBucketHead(node);

5114 case HasOwnProperty: {
5115 SpeculateCellOperand object(this, node->child1());
5116 GPRTemporary uniquedStringImpl(this);
5117 GPRTemporary temp(this);
5118 GPRTemporary hash(this);
5119 GPRTemporary structureID(this);
5120 GPRTemporary result(this);
5121
5122 std::optional<SpeculateCellOperand> keyAsCell;
5123 std::optional<JSValueOperand> keyAsValue;
5124 GPRReg keyGPR;
5125 if (node->child2().useKind() == UntypedUse) {
5126 keyAsValue.emplace(this, node->child2());
5127 keyGPR = keyAsValue->gpr();
5128 } else {
5129 ASSERT(node->child2().useKind() == StringUse || node->child2().useKind() == SymbolUse);
5130 keyAsCell.emplace(this, node->child2());
5131 keyGPR = keyAsCell->gpr();
5132 }
5133
5134 GPRReg objectGPR = object.gpr();
5135 GPRReg implGPR = uniquedStringImpl.gpr();
5136 GPRReg tempGPR = temp.gpr();
5137 GPRReg hashGPR = hash.gpr();
5138 GPRReg structureIDGPR = structureID.gpr();
5139 GPRReg resultGPR = result.gpr();
5140
5141 speculateObject(node->child1());
5142
5143 MacroAssembler::JumpList slowPath;
5144 switch (node->child2().useKind()) {
5145 case SymbolUse: {
5146 speculateSymbol(node->child2(), keyGPR);
5147 m_jit.loadPtr(MacroAssembler::Address(keyGPR, Symbol::offsetOfSymbolImpl()), implGPR);
5148 break;
5149 }
5150 case StringUse: {
5151 speculateString(node->child2(), keyGPR);
5152 m_jit.loadPtr(MacroAssembler::Address(keyGPR, JSString::offsetOfValue()), implGPR);
5153 slowPath.append(m_jit.branchIfRopeStringImpl(implGPR));
5154 slowPath.append(m_jit.branchTest32(
5155 MacroAssembler::Zero, MacroAssembler::Address(implGPR, StringImpl::flagsOffset()),
5156 MacroAssembler::TrustedImm32(StringImpl::flagIsAtom())));
5157 break;
5158 }
5159 case UntypedUse: {
5160 slowPath.append(m_jit.branchIfNotCell(JSValueRegs(keyGPR)));
5161 auto isNotString = m_jit.branchIfNotString(keyGPR);
5162 m_jit.loadPtr(MacroAssembler::Address(keyGPR, JSString::offsetOfValue()), implGPR);
5163 slowPath.append(m_jit.branchIfRopeStringImpl(implGPR));
5164 slowPath.append(m_jit.branchTest32(
5165 MacroAssembler::Zero, MacroAssembler::Address(implGPR, StringImpl::flagsOffset()),
5166 MacroAssembler::TrustedImm32(StringImpl::flagIsAtom())));
5167 auto hasUniquedImpl = m_jit.jump();
5168
5169 isNotString.link(&m_jit);
5170 slowPath.append(m_jit.branchIfNotSymbol(keyGPR));
5171 m_jit.loadPtr(MacroAssembler::Address(keyGPR, Symbol::offsetOfSymbolImpl()), implGPR);
5172
5173 hasUniquedImpl.link(&m_jit);
5174 break;
5175 }
5176 default:
5177 RELEASE_ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
5178 }
5179
5180 // Note that we don't test if the hash is zero here. AtomStringImpl's can't have a zero
5181 // hash, however, a SymbolImpl may. But, because this is a cache, we don't care. We only
5182 // ever load the result from the cache if the cache entry matches what we are querying for.
5183 // So we either get super lucky and use zero for the hash and somehow collide with the entity
5184 // we're looking for, or we realize we're comparing against another entity, and go to the
5185 // slow path anyways.
5186 m_jit.load32(MacroAssembler::Address(implGPR, UniquedStringImpl::flagsOffset()), hashGPR);
5187 m_jit.urshift32(MacroAssembler::TrustedImm32(StringImpl::s_flagCount), hashGPR);
5188 m_jit.load32(MacroAssembler::Address(objectGPR, JSCell::structureIDOffset()), structureIDGPR);
5189 m_jit.add32(structureIDGPR, hashGPR);
5190 m_jit.and32(TrustedImm32(HasOwnPropertyCache::mask), hashGPR);
5191 if (hasOneBitSet(sizeof(HasOwnPropertyCache::Entry))) // is a power of 2
5192 m_jit.lshift32(TrustedImm32(getLSBSet(sizeof(HasOwnPropertyCache::Entry))), hashGPR);
5193 else
5194 m_jit.mul32(TrustedImm32(sizeof(HasOwnPropertyCache::Entry)), hashGPR, hashGPR);
5195 ASSERT(vm().hasOwnPropertyCache());
5196 m_jit.move(TrustedImmPtr(vm().hasOwnPropertyCache()), tempGPR);
5197 slowPath.append(m_jit.branchPtr(MacroAssembler::NotEqual,
5198 MacroAssembler::BaseIndex(tempGPR, hashGPR, MacroAssembler::TimesOne, HasOwnPropertyCache::Entry::offsetOfImpl()), implGPR));
5199 m_jit.load8(MacroAssembler::BaseIndex(tempGPR, hashGPR, MacroAssembler::TimesOne, HasOwnPropertyCache::Entry::offsetOfResult()), resultGPR);
5200 m_jit.load32(MacroAssembler::BaseIndex(tempGPR, hashGPR, MacroAssembler::TimesOne, HasOwnPropertyCache::Entry::offsetOfStructureID()), tempGPR);
5201 slowPath.append(m_jit.branch32(MacroAssembler::NotEqual, tempGPR, structureIDGPR));
5202 auto done = m_jit.jump();
5203
5204 slowPath.link(&m_jit);
5205 silentSpillAllRegisters(resultGPR);
5206 callOperation(operationHasOwnProperty, resultGPR, TrustedImmPtr::weakPointer(m_graph, m_graph.globalObjectFor(node->origin.semantic)), objectGPR, keyGPR);
5207 silentFillAllRegisters();
5208 m_jit.exceptionCheck();
5209
5210 done.link(&m_jit);
5211 m_jit.or32(TrustedImm32(JSValue::ValueFalse), resultGPR);
5212 jsValueResult(resultGPR, node, DataFormatJSBoolean);
5213 break;
5214 }

5218 break;

5359 case DataViewGetFloat:
5360 case DataViewGetInt: {
5361 SpeculateCellOperand dataView(this, node->child1());
5362 GPRReg dataViewGPR = dataView.gpr();
5363 speculateDataViewObject(node->child1(), dataViewGPR);
5364
5365 SpeculateInt32Operand index(this, node->child2());
5366 GPRReg indexGPR = index.gpr();
5367
5368 GPRTemporary temp1(this);
5369 GPRReg t1 = temp1.gpr();
5370 GPRTemporary temp2(this);
5371 GPRReg t2 = temp2.gpr();
5372
5373 std::optional<SpeculateBooleanOperand> isLittleEndianOperand;
5374 if (node->child3())
5375 isLittleEndianOperand.emplace(this, node->child3());
5376 GPRReg isLittleEndianGPR = isLittleEndianOperand ? isLittleEndianOperand->gpr() : InvalidGPRReg;
5377
5378 DataViewData data = node->dataViewData();
5379
5380 m_jit.zeroExtend32ToWord(indexGPR, t2);
5381 if (data.byteSize > 1)
5382 m_jit.add64(TrustedImm32(data.byteSize - 1), t2);
5383 m_jit.load32(MacroAssembler::Address(dataViewGPR, JSArrayBufferView::offsetOfLength()), t1);
5384 speculationCheck(OutOfBounds, JSValueRegs(), node,
5385 m_jit.branch64(MacroAssembler::AboveOrEqual, t2, t1));
5386
5387 m_jit.loadPtr(JITCompiler::Address(dataViewGPR, JSArrayBufferView::offsetOfVector()), t2);
5388 cageTypedArrayStorage(dataViewGPR, t2, false);
5389
5390 m_jit.zeroExtend32ToWord(indexGPR, t1);
5391 auto baseIndex = JITCompiler::BaseIndex(t2, t1, MacroAssembler::TimesOne);
5392
5393 if (node->op() == DataViewGetInt) {
5394 switch (data.byteSize) {
5395 case 1:
5396 if (data.isSigned)
5397 m_jit.load8SignedExtendTo32(baseIndex, t2);
5398 else
5399 m_jit.load8(baseIndex, t2);
5400 strictInt32Result(t2, node);
5401 break;
5402 case 2: {
5403 auto emitLittleEndianLoad = [&] {
5404 if (data.isSigned)
5405 m_jit.load16SignedExtendTo32(baseIndex, t2);
5406 else
5407 m_jit.load16(baseIndex, t2);
5408 };
5409 auto emitBigEndianLoad = [&] {
5410 m_jit.load16(baseIndex, t2);
5411 m_jit.byteSwap16(t2);
5412 if (data.isSigned)
5413 m_jit.signExtend16To32(t2, t2);
5414 };
5415
5416 if (data.isLittleEndian == TriState::False)
5417 emitBigEndianLoad();
5418 else if (data.isLittleEndian == TriState::True)
5419 emitLittleEndianLoad();
5420 else {
5421 RELEASE_ASSERT(isLittleEndianGPR != InvalidGPRReg);
5422 auto isBigEndian = m_jit.branchTest32(MacroAssembler::Zero, isLittleEndianGPR, TrustedImm32(1));
5423 emitLittleEndianLoad();
5424 auto done = m_jit.jump();
5425 isBigEndian.link(&m_jit);
5426 emitBigEndianLoad();
5427 done.link(&m_jit);
5428 }
5429 strictInt32Result(t2, node);
5430 break;
5431 }
5432 case 4: {
5433 m_jit.load32(baseIndex, t2);
5434
5435 if (data.isLittleEndian == TriState::False)
5436 m_jit.byteSwap32(t2);
5437 else if (data.isLittleEndian == TriState::Indeterminate) {
5438 RELEASE_ASSERT(isLittleEndianGPR != InvalidGPRReg);
5439 auto isLittleEndian = m_jit.branchTest32(MacroAssembler::NonZero, isLittleEndianGPR, TrustedImm32(1));
5440 m_jit.byteSwap32(t2);
5441 isLittleEndian.link(&m_jit);
5442 }
5443
5444 if (data.isSigned)
5445 strictInt32Result(t2, node);
5446 else
5447 strictInt52Result(t2, node);
5448 break;
5449 }
5450 default:
5451 RELEASE_ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
5452 }
5453 } else {
5454 FPRTemporary result(this);
5455 FPRReg resultFPR = result.fpr();
5456
5457 switch (data.byteSize) {
5458 case 4: {
5459 auto emitLittleEndianCode = [&] {
5460 m_jit.loadFloat(baseIndex, resultFPR);
5461 m_jit.convertFloatToDouble(resultFPR, resultFPR);
5462 };
5463
5464 auto emitBigEndianCode = [&] {
5465 m_jit.load32(baseIndex, t2);
5466 m_jit.byteSwap32(t2);
5467 m_jit.move32ToFloat(t2, resultFPR);
5468 m_jit.convertFloatToDouble(resultFPR, resultFPR);
5469 };
5470
5471 if (data.isLittleEndian == TriState::True)
5472 emitLittleEndianCode();
5473 else if (data.isLittleEndian == TriState::False)
5474 emitBigEndianCode();
5475 else {
5476 RELEASE_ASSERT(isLittleEndianGPR != InvalidGPRReg);
5477 auto isBigEndian = m_jit.branchTest32(MacroAssembler::Zero, isLittleEndianGPR, TrustedImm32(1));
5478 emitLittleEndianCode();
5479 auto done = m_jit.jump();
5480 isBigEndian.link(&m_jit);
5481 emitBigEndianCode();
5482 done.link(&m_jit);
5483 }
5484
5485 break;
5486 }
5487 case 8: {
5488 auto emitLittleEndianCode = [&] {
5489 m_jit.loadDouble(baseIndex, resultFPR);
5490 };
5491
5492 auto emitBigEndianCode = [&] {
5493 m_jit.load64(baseIndex, t2);
5494 m_jit.byteSwap64(t2);
5495 m_jit.move64ToDouble(t2, resultFPR);
5496 };
5497
5498 if (data.isLittleEndian == TriState::True)
5499 emitLittleEndianCode();
5500 else if (data.isLittleEndian == TriState::False)
5501 emitBigEndianCode();
5502 else {
5503 RELEASE_ASSERT(isLittleEndianGPR != InvalidGPRReg);
5504 auto isBigEndian = m_jit.branchTest32(MacroAssembler::Zero, isLittleEndianGPR, TrustedImm32(1));
5505 emitLittleEndianCode();
5506 auto done = m_jit.jump();
5507 isBigEndian.link(&m_jit);
5508 emitBigEndianCode();
5509 done.link(&m_jit);
5510 }
5511
5512 break;
5513 }
5514 default:
5515 RELEASE_ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
5516 }
5517
5518 doubleResult(resultFPR, node);
5519 }
5520
5521 break;
5522 }

5539 std::optional<SpeculateInt32Operand> int32Value;
5540 std::optional<FPRTemporary> fprTemporary;

5569 GPRTemporary temp1(this);
5570 GPRReg t1 = temp1.gpr();
5571 GPRTemporary temp2(this);

5575

5592 auto baseIndex = JITCompiler::BaseIndex(t2, t1, MacroAssembler::TimesOne);
5593
5594 if (data.isFloatingPoint) {
5595 RELEASE_ASSERT(valueFPR != InvalidFPRReg);
5596 if (data.byteSize == 4) {
5597 RELEASE_ASSERT(tempFPR != InvalidFPRReg);
5598 m_jit.convertDoubleToFloat(valueFPR, tempFPR);
5599
5600 auto emitLittleEndianCode = [&] {
5601 m_jit.storeFloat(tempFPR, baseIndex);
5602 };
5603
5604 auto emitBigEndianCode = [&] {
5605 m_jit.moveFloatTo32(tempFPR, t3);
